https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/miZZ9iUNrzX2hhHJzx8yqjGzpmw.jpg Go behind the scenes of StarKid Homecoming: the biggest reunion of StarKids ever! Over the course of three wild days, almost everyone who's even been in a StarKid show came to Los Angeles to celebrate a decade of A Very Potter Musical and StarKid shows. This featurette (unlocked as part of the 10niversary Kickstarter) takes you backstage and into rehearsals as the whole show came together. 10umentary: Behind the Scenes of StarKid Homecoming
